    </div>

    <h3>The Dates</h3>
    <p>
        Matching: mid-June-ish<br/>
        Shipping: Anytime after Matching, but before August 1 (unless your match requests later)<br/>
    </p>

    <h3>The Rules</h3>

        <b>Standard</b>
        <ul style="margin-top: 5px">
            <li>Minimum 128oz</li>
            <li>Minimum 8 unique beers</li>
            <li>Average rating for the best 128oz must be 4.0</li>
        </ul>

        <b>Pro</b>
        <ul style="margin-top: 5px">
            <li>Minimum 160oz</li>
            <li>Minimum 10 unique beers</li>
            <li>Average rating for the best 160oz must be 4.0</li>
            <li>At least 2 Lagers<sup>*</sup> and 2 Farmhouse beers<sup>**</sup></li>
        </ul>
        <div style="font-size: .9em"><sup>*</sup> "Lager" includes any bottom fermented or cold conditioned beer.  This includes Pilsners, Kölsches, and High Life. Ship Baltic Porters at your own risk.</div>
        <div style="font-size: .9em"><sup>**</sup> "Farmhouse" includes traditional farmhouse styles as well as wild ales.</div>
    
